cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL. 

The paper deals with 3D object detection from LiDAR point cloud, which is a problem in computer vision and robotics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes a novel neural network architecture, which involves learning from data and making predictions, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. Additionally, the paper uses supervised learning and explores the spatial relationship of the pooled intra-object part locations, indicating the possibility of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) categories.
